caption.title: Statistical information on the significantly differentially expressed proteins from hemocytes.
caption.p: MSstats output table including the protein identifier, label (group comparison), log 2 fold change, standard error, T value, degree of freedom, raw p-value and adjusted p-value based on Benjamini and Hochberg method to collect multiple testing issue and further control false discovery rate (adj.pvalue).
